Vea Rainbow Bedroom Den Blackout Curtain Room Shade Cloth for Bedroom & Dark Shading

Add a splash of color and privacy to your child’s room with the Vea Rainbow Bedroom Den Blackout Curtain. Designed for boys and girls, this curtain provides excellent shading and light control, creating a cozy and playful den for bedrooms, playrooms, or study areas.

Available in multiple styles, including cloth or yarn, hook type or perforated, and a variety of rainbow-themed colors (blue or pink), it allows customization to match your child’s room décor. Sized from Width 1.5 × Height 2.0m up to Width 4.0 × Height 2.7m, or custom sizes on request, it fits a wide range of room layouts.

  • Multiple styles: cloth or yarn, hook type or perforated

  • Various size options to suit different room dimensions

  • Creates a cozy den or private play space

products.body_html:
Veridian Full Blackout Curtains European Style Decor Semi-shading for Bedroom & Living Room

Elevate your bedroom décor with the Veridian Green Bedroom Full Blackout Curtains. Crafted from a combination of cloth and gauze, these European-style curtains feature a charming heart-shaped pattern that adds elegance while providing semi-shading for privacy. Ideal for bedrooms, living rooms, or any space where you want style and functionality combined.

How to Use:

  • Measure your window to select the correct size and hook style.

  • Hang using ordinary hook, punching, or Korean fold hook as preferred.

  • Adjust to block light partially and add a decorative touch.

  • Gently hand wash or dry clean to maintain quality.

Specifications:

  • Material: Cloth Curtain + Gauze Curtain

  • Pattern: Heart-shaped

  • Style: European

  • Color Options: Green Cloth, Green Yarn, Blue-gray Cloth, Blue Yarn

  • Type: Semi-shading Blackout Curtain

  • Size Options: 1 meter increments (processing fee not included)

Why You'll Love It:

  • Heart-shaped pattern adds decorative charm

  • Provides semi-shading and enhances privacy

  • European style complements modern and classic interiors

  • Flexible hook options for easy installation

  • Perfect for bedrooms, living rooms, or decorative spaces
